title: My Missing Contributions to the Tuesday Night Bible Study
description:
Commentary on the Bible study with @faturechi and @Almond Tree after I left the discussion. Several topics were discussed that I have made videos about previously. 


Videos about Adam and Eve

https://youtu.be/BaxmWfA4OcE

 https://youtu.be/AJnf9xT8shQ

Videos about the epigenetic transmission of sin

https://youtu.be/Aw2DfahtXkQ

https://youtu.be/LP7YPBZcAGY

https://youtu.be/LFxjp2z4liY

Videos about the virgin birth 

https://youtu.be/ebGZxLnmuQs

https://youtu.be/MztXE2YBWmU

https://youtu.be/Q-q7WDxci9c

The last two videos are also tied to a 45 page paper I wrote about the early stories in genesis prior to the Tower of Babel, which explains why the virgin birth is more important as a sign to the nations outside of Israel. 


Naked Bible podcast on the astronomical dating of Jesus birth

https://youtu.be/3rFznc3Af64
